summary: Before season 2 did u think cyrus was gay
question: Before season 2 did u think cyrus was gay
answer: Yes! I was one of the few people who read the New York Times article on March 10, 2017 (when the first episode was released online) which leaked that “a boy is coming to terms with his sexuality”. So after watching the second episode, when Cyrus meets Jonah, it was pretty easy to tell which of the boys that article was referring to.

summary: What was your first Andi Mack ship?
question: What was your first Andi Mack ship?
answer:
My first Ship was Tyrus and also jandi…

Omg and also Muffy

I got into the show due to Cyrus’ storyline as whenever I hear about a show I sort of stalk the wiki page and when I checked it out Jonah was listed as “potential crush” for Cyrus.

When I then watched it I never shipped Jyrus it was always one sided and the relationship got better the more it turned to friendship on Cyrus’ end imo.

And Jandi was good at first but then I realised it was kind of toxic because she idolised an idea of him and he wasn’t the best boyfriend really and the whole “I’m not into labels” thing and Andi realising she was sort of into an idea not a person yanno? Like it works better as friends but at first I saw it pushing Jandi and was like guess that’s the ship 🤷🏼‍♀️

I loved Muffy so much and honestly because I never watched season 2 fully I didn’t realise till I got into tumblr that they had a sort of “break up” episode and I just thought Marty had randomly disappeared 🤷🏼‍♀️

I didn’t watch it whole heartedly till Tyrus came about and I saw “potential crush” on this boy TJ and was like hmmmmm. And I kept track of the TJ episodes and by the finale of season 2 I was a solid shipper

I didn’t actually start properly watching like every single episode till 3x06 and that’s so recent 😭😂

I need to fully watch season 2 I still haven’t seen all of it, and I also haven’t seen 3x05. I watched 1-4 because I was waiting for TJ to come back and then forgot about 5 but then 6 happened 😏

THEN JOINED THIS HELL HOLE AND NEVER LOOKED BACK.

To summarise Muffy and Jandi at first but Tyrus was my first full and Proper ship
